Vodafone Sees Smartphone Data Growth in India, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-09-05T05:28:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-05/vodafone-sees-smartphone-data-growth-in-india-handelsblatt-says.html
Vodafone Group Plc (VOD)  expects data
sales to smartphone users to drive rapid growth in  India ,
 Handelsblatt  reported, citing an interview with Chief Executive
Officer Vittorio Colao.  Data sales will help the company’s India unit become
profitable soon, the newspaper reported today. The unit is
Vodafone’s fastest-growing in terms of new customers, according
to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
 nkresge@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net  